<p><a href="/mediawiki/index.php?title=Special:Upload&amp;wpDestFile=OpsBridge2019.02Or2.jpg" class="new" title="File:OpsBridge2019.02Or2.jpg">File:OpsBridge2019.02Or2.jpg</a>
