<ol><li>Download the oracle instant client package from the link <a target="1" rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/topics/linuxx86-64soft-092277.html">http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/topics/linuxx86-64soft-092277.html</a> in the master node.</li>
<li>Install the same: <br> rpm -i oracle-instantclient12.1-basic-12.1.0.2.0-1.x86_64.rpm</li>
<li>Make the following environment variable settings to use the sqlplus client: <br>LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib/oracle/12.1/client64/lib/:${LD_LIBRARY_PATH} <br> export LD_LIBRARY_PATH<br>PATH=/usr/lib/oracle/12.1/client64/bin/:${PATH}<br>export PATH<br>SQLPATH=/usr/lib/oracle/12.1/client64/lib/:${SQLPATH}<br>export SQLPATH<br>NLS_LANG=AMERICAN_AMERICA.UTF8<br>export NLS_LANG<br>set ORACLE_SID=ORCL</li>
<li>Once the client is installed, get into sqlplus. Create the user role in oracle like: <br> create role dbuser identified by dbpassword;</li>
<li>Run the following sql commands:<br> GRANT CONNECT, RESOURCE, DBA TO dbuser; <br>GRANT CREATE SESSION GRANT ANY PRIVILEGE TO dbuser; <br> GRANT UNLIMITED TABLESPACE TO dbuser; <br> CREATE SCHEMA cdf_idm USER dbuser IDENTIFIED BY dbpassword<br>CREATE USER &lt;user_schema&gt; IDENTIFIED BY &lt;user_password&gt; DEFAULT TABLESPACE USERS<br>TEMPORARY TABLESPACE TEMP<br>QUOTA UNLIMITED ON USERS;<br>GRANT "CONNECT" TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT CREATE SEQUENCE TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT CREATE TABLE TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT CREATE TRIGGER TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT CREATE VIEW TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT CREATE PROCEDURE TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT CREATE TYPE TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>GRANT SELECT ON sys.props$ TO &lt;user_schema&gt;;<br>ALTER USER &lt;user_schema&gt; DEFAULT ROLE ALL;</li></ol>
<p><br>
</p>
